        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Modes are a new type of Workspace that store all of the native Obsidian Editor, Files & Links, \n        and Appearance settings. Enabling this will add a new mode switcher to the status bar that will allow you\n        to save, apply, rename, and switch between modes.",
          "target": "模式是一种新型的工作区，它存储所有原生的 Obsidian 编辑器、文件与链接以及外观设置。启用此功能将在状态栏添加一个新的模式切换器，允许您保存、应用、重命名和切换模式。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "This option will auto save your current workspace on any layout change.\n         Leave this disabled if you want full control over when your workspace is saved.",
          "target": "此选项将在布局更改时自动保存当前工作区。如果您希望完全控制工作区的保存时机，请禁用此选项。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Let the OS determine the light/dark mode setting when switching modes. This setting can only be used if Workspace Modes is enabled.",
          "target": "切换模式时，让操作系统决定浅色/深色模式设置。此设置仅在启用工作区模式时可用。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "When switching between Modes with different Experimental Live Preview settings, reload Obsidian in order for the setting\n                change to take effect. ⚠️Note: Obsidian will reload automatically after changing workspaces, if needed, without any prompts.",
          "target": "当在具有不同实验性实时预览设置的模式之间切换时，需要重新加载 Obsidian 才能使设置更改生效。⚠️注意：如果需要，Obsidian 会在更改工作区后自动重新加载，无需任何提示。"
        },
